    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Description\n\ntaplo no longer functions and crashes immediately on any edit to a .toml file due to a mismatch in both the URL and the schema store catalog schema. It should be removed from `nvim-lspconfig`. It is also installed by LazyVim as part of the extras.lang.toml plugin.\n\nSee: \n\nhttps://github.com/tamasfe/taplo/issues/799#issuecomment-4382152371\nhttps://github.com/tamasfe/taplo/pull/866\n\nRecommended replacement:\n\nhttps://github.com/tombi-toml/tombi\nhttps://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/blob/master/lsp/tombi.lua",
    "closed_at": null,
    "closed_by": null,
    "comment_data": [
